Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  马上就要到暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要去海边？
