Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  把她吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  快告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别墅在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是海浪的味道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去游泳喽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  不是来玩的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本想让大家住在更宽敞的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只能借来这个最小的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最小的？这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我说过不用准备了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主床啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我一直在说  尽量普通点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可总是不能理解我的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有段时间没用了  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点担心能不能很好地运作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  看上去没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  唯和律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半路上就不见人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了她们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以前的轻音部在学园祭上的LIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间在活动室里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我们要强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了之后  总有种不想输给他们的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就提出了合宿  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！  一起玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！练习呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了  两位也快点哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  你准备去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正难得来次  稍微玩会儿的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂到这个无人岛已经两周了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冲上来时我还以为完蛋了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这倒也算过得挺开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…发现宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们乱设定些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:37.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（爆CUP）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一击！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯！我们去游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：It's a PONY=_,=||）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你们画了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来就已经做成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕不怕不怕不怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去医生那里检查的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现膝盖上密密麻麻都是藤壶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:23.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（出自都市传说「藤壶与膝盖」，大意为：\N在海边岩礁摔倒后划破膝盖的话膝盖骨内侧就会长满藤壶）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝进海水啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于到达黄金岛Zipangu啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Zipangu  欧洲对日本的旧称，历史上哥伦布最初是以黄金岛\NZipangu为目标出航，并不知道自己发现的是美洲大陆）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候拿来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来一次海边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛快地玩一下  来这里的意义就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！练习！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全忘光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪律你说要去玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得最欢的家伙又是哪位啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～撑死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板冰冰凉的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像在海浪中漂游一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  你靠边一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Rcat：该出手时就出手啊你XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  今天还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了练习才来这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来律啊  最近你是不是变胖了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是肚子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为最近都没怎么敲鼓啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经拿不动吉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把吉他太重了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不早说了让你挑把轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁！说要买这把吉他的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板也快变得热起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚滚滚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会弄脏的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又变凉快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这样到学园祭的时候怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早说了嘛  搞个女仆咖啡店不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要开鬼屋啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你是一点也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看澪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊  突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没几个人比澪更适合穿女仆装哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色长袜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯白围裙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上女仆头带！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌啊萌啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾{\fe1\fnWebdings}Y{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj:京A乃太犯规XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上这样的台词啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑啦  玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律队员…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩完之后给我好好练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最后一首！来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Yeah～Oh Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？已经没啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预算有限嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还有机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武道馆公演上我们可以尽情的磅磅磅磅磅！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武道馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  那是我们决定好的目标啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到时候我要粉红的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  因为很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小孩子气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得粉红有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是武道馆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要达到这种程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不过这首曲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你们好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧——！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁带翻到B面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听见没听见没听见没听见…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤壶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝盖骨鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦～不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩过火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没什么妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌啊萌啊～啾{\fe1\fnWebdings}Y{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  但刚才那首曲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj:这就是有着绝对音感的天才唯XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒  很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:19:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不太懂「咪嗡～」那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咪嗡」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个应该是推弦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（推弦（Bending）：吉他演奏技巧之一，通过按弦的手指\N将琴弦推起改变音品原来的音高，チョーキング为日式英语，\N英语中Bending读音为ベンディング）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choking？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（与Bending的日语发音相同）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推弦就是在弹出声音时把弦推拉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个总感觉超怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似戳到她笑点上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（戳笑点（ツボ）与藤壶（フジツボ）同音，\N但戳笑点的ツボ是指「指圧のツボ」，并非壶的意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤壶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到连露天浴池都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能并不用那么担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就应该多玩下才对啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刘海好长～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过意外的可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过「意外」是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起…顺口就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你看得懂吗？好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  只要把无名指弹出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然音乐真是不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第一次和大家合奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了小澪说要来合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪这家伙害羞咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！泡晕了而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说不是了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵  澪生气啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～好可怕～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿的照片洗出来啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便还有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底片交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是数码的…没底片…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  澪  要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:22:02.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（目标  武道馆!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't say「You are lazy」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:16.78,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だって本当はcrazy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:22.07,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}白鳥たちはそう　見えないとこでバタ足するんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:27.38,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}本能に従順 忠実　翻弄も重々承知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:32.86,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}前途洋々だし…だからたまに休憩しちゃうんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:43.58,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}近道あればそれが王道　はしょれる翼もあれば上等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:53.32,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ヤバ 爪割れた　グルーで補修した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:58.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}それだけでなんか達成感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:03.95,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大事なのは自分　かわいがること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:09.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分を愛さなきゃ　他人も愛せない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:13.12,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't say「You are lazy」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だって本当はcrazy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:21.09,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能ある鷹はそう　見えないとこにピック隠すんです
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:26.39,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想像に一生懸命　現実は絶体絶命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:32.11,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}発展途中だし…だから不意にピッチ外れるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't say「You are lazy」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:16.78,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因为其实是crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:22.07,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}白鸟们在暗处浅打水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:27.38,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}忠实顺从本能　明知重重颠簸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:32.86,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}前途光明…所以稍事休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:43.58,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}近道即王道　折翼更上等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:53.32,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}利爪破裂　以胶修补
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:58.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}如此就有成就感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:03.95,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怜惜自己很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:09.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不爱自己何谈爱他人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:13.12,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't say「You are lazy」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因为其实是crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:21.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能乐者敛其锋芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:26.39,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拼命想像　现实却一筹莫展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:32.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}还在发展途中…所以会意外地走音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然列表上没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你有弹过吉他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.02,0:23:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是以前的朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:24:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是澪前几天在箱子里翻出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.18,0:24:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是以前轻音部的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！不愧是和和
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾问呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾问？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:09.70,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}#5　　顾问!


